studies for finite element method, first target is 1D version.
in progress...

there are some prerequirements for FEM.
1. solve asymmetric sparse linear system
2. numerical integration

so as the first step, implemented BiCGSTAB method for 1.


[fukuoka@selene71 bicgstab]$ make
ifort -g -O3 -mavx -fopenmp bicgstab.F90 -o a.out
[fukuoka@selene71 bicgstab]$ ./a.out
